          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>From the NUMBER LINE</p><p>80 + –55 = 25 (or 80 – 55 = 25)</p><p>CHIP BOARD</p><p>On the chip board, you would need 80 black chips. Then you add 55 red chips to get 25. </p><p>          80 + –55 =</p><p>(25 + 55) + –55 =</p><p>25 + (55 + –55) = </p><p>              25 + 0 = 25</p>"
